OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with a little
OL,6,Flight and patchy rain, otherwise dry.
OL,7,FThis afternoon will be dry with some
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells breaking
OL,9,Fthrough. Still warm in sheltered parts
OL,10,Fof the east, otherwise cooler than
OL,11,Fyesterday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMainly dry this evening but
OL,14,Frain spreading to the Western Isles.
OL,15,FThen rain will spread across all parts
OL,16,Fovernight, becoming drier along the
OL,17,Fwest coast later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
