OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FOvernight rain clearing
OL,6,Fduring the morning. Then bright spells
OL,7,Fand scattered showers, these turning
OL,8,Fheavy in the west later. Colder than
OL,9,Fof late.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry and
OL,12,Fbright for most of Friday but
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain spreading northeast
OL,14,Fin the evening. Mainly dry Saturday, a
OL,15,Ffew showers in the west. Breezy with
OL,16,Fshowers on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
